{"tid":719092,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人父母好鐘意睇淡？","createTime":"2018-06-27T07:42:56.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-27T11:59:16.000Z","uid":58998,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"0e1ee4105bcbd859c879d1153e6929bb8ae2b1a6","tid":719092,"uid":58998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T07:42:56.000Z","msg":"明明自己就一定買唔起，又日日望個樓市跌，見到屢創高位，又話咩美國就快加息，又話咩個市遲早大跌<br />\n又話咩我未見過以前幾慘，以前97見好多銀主盤好多人負資產跌樓<br />\n都講咗成十年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0358eb3069fb4b0840aecb353afbb93a3f7df44c","tid":719092,"uid":173159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T11:13:57.000Z","msg":"當年我大伯就係因為咁破左產<br />\n隔左咁多年都未翻到身<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n潮退既時候就知邊個無著泳褲"},{"pid":"1ade25f3075daf7edc31f963d710d1b8b2522313","tid":719092,"uid":45440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T11:17:17.000Z","msg":"一代傳一代，到時你冇樓俾個仔，又係揾睇淡黎自我安慰"},{"pid":"0b744a90b954e841e01ca3e31aed5f37dbafc7b0","tid":719092,"uid":56698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T11:31:30.000Z","msg":"我老豆老母都係，所以佢地依世都唔會有得退休<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e1f7cbf11005a3fc90fc9738f05da082392d314","tid":719092,"uid":56698,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"1ade25f3075daf7edc31f963d710d1b8b2522313","tid":719092,"uid":45440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T11:17:17.000Z","msg":"一代傳一代，到時你冇樓俾個仔，又係揾睇淡黎自我安慰"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T11:32:04.000Z","msg":"所以一定唔會有下一代，害撚死佢"},{"pid":"ca1d10d7d863e415988459b28b3a3ea6a8543f92","tid":719092,"uid":58998,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T11:41:07.000Z","msg":"依幾日見個市跌佢都好開心，話啲老闆炒孖展就快輸到跌樓了"},{"pid":"09218b97a52bdb1bbb4779f076cdcb35183d6db3","tid":719092,"uid":1367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T11:51: